When you reach a Druid level specified in the Circle of
the Old Ways Spells table, you thereafter always have
the listed spells prepared.Circle of the Old Ways Spells
Druid Level Prepared Spells
3 Ancestral {@spell Guidance} *, {@spell Barkskin}, Shield of
Faith, {@spell Shillelagh}, {@spell Spike Growth}
5 {@spell Magic Circle}, {@spell Plant Growth}
7 {@spell Freedom of Movement}, {@spell Private Sanctum}
9 {@spell Awaken}, {@spell Tree Stride}

The magic of your patron ensures you always have
certain spells ready; when you reach a Warlock level
specified in the Great Fool Spells table, you thereafter
always have the listed spells prepared.Great Fool Spells
Warlock Level Spells
3 {@spell Disguise Self}, Hideous Laughter, {@spell Rope Trick},
{@spell Spiritual Weapon}, {@spell Vicious Mockery}
5 {@spell Blink}, {@spell Stinking Cloud}
7 {@spell Phantasmal Killer}, Puppet Master *
9 {@spell Arcane Hand}, {@spell Mislead}
